INSERT INTO wp_posts (post_title, post_content, post_name, post_date, post_date_gmt, post_modified, post_modified_gmt, post_author, post_status, post_type) VALUES ('TAPE', '<img align=\"right\" alt=\"\" hspace=\"5\" src=\"http://localhost:3000/wp-content/themes/wildproject/images/performances/2017-TAPE.jpg\" vspace=\"5\"/>
<p>Fractal Productions Presents...</p>
<p class=\"showTitle\">TAPE</p>
<h2 class=\"firstheader\">showtimes &amp; tickets:</h2>
<p>February 10-12<br/>
			Friday &amp; Saturday @ 7PM<br/>
			Saturday &amp; Sunday @ 2PM</p>
<p>written by Stephen Belber<br/>
			featuring Chase Crandell, Jay Stuart and Meredith Bechtel</p>
<p>Two former highs school buddies see each other for the first time in years. What starts friendly ends up with Vince trying to convince Jon that he raped his girlfriend in high school. Once Jon admits to the wrong doing, Vince pulls out a tape recorder and threatens to tell the police. Amy then shows up, thinking she\'s only there to visit her ex boyfriend, Vince, and she changes the entire outcome of the situation.</p>
